OL,3,CStates of Guernsey rejects proposed
OL,4,Cincome tax rise but paves way for GST
OL,6,FGuernsey politicians have thrown out
OL,7,Fthe island's proposed 2p in the pound
OL,8,Frise in income tax as part of the 2025
OL,9,FBudget but have agreed to make plans
OL,10,Ffor a Goods and Services Tax (GST) in
OL,11,F2027.
OL,13,FThe decision followed four days of
OL,14,Fdeputies debating 22 amendments to the
OL,15,FBudget to try and plug a #100 million
OL,16,Fshortfall in funding.
