OL,3,CStates of Guernsey rejects proposed
OL,4,Cincome tax rise but paves way for GST
OL,6,FHowever, he warned that without the
OL,7,Festimated #34 million pounds of extra
OL,8,Frevenue, the next States will find
OL,9,Fitself firefighting resources which
OL,10,Fare under increasing pressure from the
OL,11,Fageing demographic.
OL,13,FHe explained: "The irony is that if
OL,14,FGST is considered the answer in
OL,15,Ffuture, it's very likely that the
OL,16,Fintroduction rate will be much higher
OL,17,Fthan it's currently proposed because
OL,18,Fof the requirement to play catch up
OL,19,Fwith the damage that we've done to
OL,20,Fpublic finances."
